skill.name: Way of the Hundred Fists
skill.description:
Generate: 8 Spirit per attack

Unleash a rapid series of punches that strikes enemies for 140% weapon damage.
skill.simpleDescription:
Generate: 8 Spirit per attack

Strike groups of enemies with a series of devastating punches.

rune.name: Fists of Fury
rune.description: Affected targets will take an additional 100% weapon damage as Holy over 5 seconds. Also adds a short dash to the first strike.
rune.simpleDescription: Perform a short dash on the first target and deal additional Holy damage over time.

skill.name: Wave of Light
skill.description:
Cost: 75 Spirit

Focuses a wave of light that crushes enemies for 829% weapon damage as Holy, followed by an additional 96% weapon damage as Holy to all enemies in a line.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 75 Spirit

Ring a mystic bell that unleashes a wave of light that crushes all enemies in its path.

rune.name: Empowered Wave
rune.description: Reduces the cost of Wave of Light to 40 Spirit.
rune.simpleDescription: Reduces the Spirit cost of Wave of Light.

skill.name: Serenity
skill.description:
Cost: 10 Spirit
Cooldown: 20 seconds

You are enveloped in a protective shield that absorbs all incoming damage for 3 seconds and grants immunity to all control impairing effects.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 10 Spirit
Cooldown: 20 seconds

Become immune to all attacks and control effects for 3 seconds.

rune.name: Peaceful Repose
rune.description: When activated, Serenity heals you for 6202 - 7752 Life.

skill.name: Exploding Palm
skill.description:
Cost: 40 Spirit

Cause a target to Bleed for 745% weapon damage as Physical over 9 seconds. If the target dies while bleeding, it explodes and deals 50% of the target's maximum Life as Physical damage to all nearby enemies.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 40 Spirit

Strike and Bleed an enemy. The enemy will explode if killed while bleeding.

rune.name: Essence Burn
rune.description: Instead of bleeding, the target will burn for 745% weapon damage as Fire over 9 seconds. If the target dies while burning, it explodes causing all nearby enemies to burn for 60% weapon damage as Fire over 3 seconds. This effect can happen multiple times.
rune.simpleDescription: Causes the target to burn. If the target dies while burning, it explodes and ignites nearby enemies.

skill.name: Seven-Sided Strike
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Dash rapidly between nearby enemies, dealing 1777% weapon damage over 7 hits.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit
Cooldown: 30 seconds

Move with blinding speed and strike nearby enemies while being immune to attacks yourself.

rune.name: Sudden Assault
rune.description: Teleport to the target, increasing damage done to 2310% weapon damage over 7 strikes.
rune.simpleDescription: Teleport to the target, increasing the damage per strike.

skill.name: Mantra of Healing
skill.description:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Recite a Mantra that causes you and your allies within 40 yards to gain increased Life regeneration by 620 Life per second. The Mantra lasts 3 minutes.

For 3 seconds after activation Mantra of Healing shrouds you and your allies with a mystical shield that absorbs up to 930 damage.

This is a Mantra. You can only have one Mantra active at a time.
skill.simpleDescription:
Cost: 50 Spirit

Increase Life regeneration for you and your allies.

Only one Mantra can be active at a time.

rune.name: Circular Breathing
rune.description: Mantra of Healing also regenerates 3 Spirit per second.

skill.name: Near Death Experience
skill.description:
When receiving fatal damage, you are instead restored to 35% of maximum Life and 35% Spirit.

This effect cannot occur twice in succession within 60 seconds.
skill.flavor: "We do not see what has been done, we only see what remains to be done." —Mantra of the Monks of Ivgorod

skill.name: Seize the Initiative
skill.description: Your Armor is increased by 50% of your Dexterity.
skill.flavor: The Monks of Ivgorod are trained to move like water—flowing freely into open spaces and crashing hard against their foes.

skill.name: One With Everything
skill.description: Your resistance to all elements is equal to your highest elemental resistance.
skill.flavor: Ice hunters brave months of frozen darkness. Desert traders bear relentless, scorching sun. This world is ours to endure.

skill.name: Poison Bolts
skill.description:
Ranged attack which deals 100% weapon damage and an additional 40% weapon damage as Poison over 2 seconds.

Cooldown: 6 seconds

skill.name: Dirty Fighting
skill.description:
Blinds enemies in front of the Scoundrel for 3 seconds.

Cooldown: 30 seconds

skill.name: Multishot
skill.description: The Scoundrel's ranged attacks fire 3 bolts at a time.
skill.simpleDescription: The Scoundrel's attacks shoot multiple bolts.

skill.name: Hysteria
skill.description: Whenever you or the Scoundrel land a Critical Hit, you both will go into hysterics, increasing all damage done by 10% for 3 seconds. This effect cannot occur more than once every 5 seconds.
skill.simpleDescription: Critical Hits cause you and the Scoundrel to temporarily deal more damage.
